
'''''The First Grader''''' ni filime yikinamico ya biografiya ya 2010 iyobowe na Justin Chadwick <ref>The First Grader (2010) - Cinema Cats <nowiki>https://cinemacats.com</nowiki> › Cinema Cats Blog</ref>. Irimo Naomie Harris, Oliver Litondo, na Tony Kgoroge<ref>The First Grader - Full Cast & Crew - TV Guide <nowiki>https://www.tvguide.com</nowiki> › movies › cast</ref> . Iyi filime ishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo ya Kimani Maruge<ref>The First Grader (2010) — The Movie Database (TMDB) <nowiki>https://www.themoviedb.org</nowiki> › movie › 47559-the-first-...</ref>, [[Kenya|umuhinzi wo muri Kenya]] wiyandikishije mu mashuri abanza afite imyaka 84 nyuma yaho guverinoma ya Kenya yatangaje ko amashuri abanza ari buntu ku isi mu 2003<ref>The First Grader (2010) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › film › cwzmq › the-first-...</ref>. 

