=== Gufata amashusho ===
[[Dosiye:Africa6_006.jpg|right|thumb| Ikibaya kinini cya Rift muri Kenya, ahabereye amashusho.]]
Producer ukomoka muri Amerika witwa Sam Feuer yasanze inkuru kurupapuro rwambere rwa LA Times ahitamo  We<ref>'The First Grader,' Justin Chadwick's Tale of Kenyan Culture <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2011/05/13 › movies › the-fir...</ref>, hanyuma, ashaka umufatanyabikorwa Richard Harding<ref>The soldier who fought for the right to go to school in Kenya <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › global-development › jun</ref>, yafatanije na BBC Films maze aha akazi Ann Peacock kwandika amashusho. Filime yakozwe n’abongereza yafatiwe  ahitwa Rift Valley muri Kenya, nubwo mbere byavuzwe ko izafatirwa muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] <ref>Watch The First Grader | Prime Video - Amazon.com <nowiki>https://www.amazon.com</nowiki> › First-Grader-Naomie-Harris</ref>. Umuyobozi Chadwick yagize ati: "Twashoboraga kuyirasa muri Afurika y'Epfo, ariko Kenya ifite izo mbaraga zidasanzwe, zidasobanutse zirangwa mu bana, ndetse n'abantu twakoraga film". <ref>Interview with director Justin Chadwick, reproduced by Soda Pictures. Theatrical Press Kit. Retrieved 2015-12-15.</ref>

